charges.charge_description: 18:287 FALSE CLAIMS &; STATEMENTS On or about November 14, 1989, defendant made a claim upon the FCIC, US Dept of Agrigculture which he knew to be false, fictitious, and fraudelent re: 225.7 acres of hybrid seed corn on Ct 1, 47.2 acres of hybrid seed corn on Ct 2, 56.9 acres of hybrid seed corn on Ct 3, 95.7 acres hybrid seed corn on Ct 4, 79.5 acres of hybrid seed corn on Ct 5, and 18.9 acres of hybrid seed corn on Ct 6 (1-2)

charges.charge_disposition: Upon motion of the Government case dismissed as to all counts as to Dft Catton (1-2)
